; Regression test for issue #1689: Error: Timelog check-out date less than corresponding check-in
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1689
;
; When a timelog has an open PROJ2 check-in at a future time (relative to --now),
; ledger creates an implicit check-out at "now" which is before the check-in,
; causing the error: Timelog check-out date less than corresponding check-in

i 2018-11-10 08:16:00 PROJ1
o 2018-11-10 08:18:00
i 2018-11-10 08:18:00 PROJ2

test --now 2018/11/10 register --time-colon -p 2018/11/10 -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Timelog check-out date less than corresponding check-in
end test
